    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885790/extras/8b31dc40335ec483fb934589f2775f51.poster.avif?t=1749993331\" width=800 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885790/extras/8b31dc40335ec483fb934589f2775f51.webm?t=1749993331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885790/extras/8b31dc40335ec483fb934589f2775f51.mp4?t=1749993331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>Badr and Jummnah are astronauts on a mission to the undiscovered areas of the galaxy, but their spacecraft is attacked by space pirates and they are forced to land on an unknown planet that they must explore and exploit what they find in it to get out of their current predicament. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885790/extras/97d84ba9154958aaa0d4a6d6ec57afeb.poster.avif?t=1749993331\" width=800 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885790/extras/97d84ba9154958aaa0d4a6d6ec57afeb.webm?t=1749993331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Untravelled Planet is a action platformer and third-person shooter game set in faraway planet. explore Open-World hostile planet a and gather resources to expand your base.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of challenges, including platforming, shooting, exploration, and puzzle-solving.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Numerous character upgrade options, complemented by a diverse selection of weapons.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An open, interconnected world featuring dozens of caves and sub-areas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive atmosphere that captures the essence of retro gaming.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885790/extras/8b31dc40335ec483fb934589f2775f51.poster.avif?t=1749993331\" width=800 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885790/extras/8b31dc40335ec483fb934589f2775f51.webm?t=1749993331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885790/extras/8b31dc40335ec483fb934589f2775f51.mp4?t=1749993331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
